		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><span class="name"><a name="20312"></a><b>Moshkiae</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails"><strong></strong><br /><br /><br />Joined: 15 Oct 2001<br />Posts: 28<br />Location: Vancouver, WA, USA</span><br /></td>
		<td class="row1" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=20312&amp;sid=ad5d9e49e18d5fb18456b1982316e7d3#20312"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Tue Nov 06, 2001 5:16 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Character listing said a Bard's main stats should be Dexteri</span></td>
				<td valign="top" align="right" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=20312&amp;sid=ad5d9e49e18d5fb18456b1982316e7d3"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
